# QimenBot 插件开发

导入：`use qimen_plugin_api::prelude::*;`

## 模块与命令

```rust
#[module(id = "my-plugin", version = "0.1.0", name = "名称", description = "描述", interceptors = [MyInterceptor])]
#[commands]
impl MyPlugin {
    #[command("描述", aliases = ["别名"], examples = ["/cmd arg"], category = "general", role = "admin", hidden)]
    async fn cmd(&self, ctx: &CommandPluginContext<'_>, args: Vec<String>) -> CommandPluginSignal { ... }

    #[notice(GroupPoke, PrivatePoke)]
    async fn on_poke(&self, ctx: &SystemPluginContext<'_>) -> SystemPluginSignal { ... }

    #[request(Friend)]
    async fn on_friend(&self, ctx: &SystemPluginContext<'_>) -> SystemPluginSignal { ... }

    #[meta(Heartbeat)]
    async fn on_heartbeat(&self) -> SystemPluginSignal { SystemPluginSignal::Continue }
}
```

## 命令 4 种签名

- `async fn cmd(&self) -> &str`
- `async fn cmd(&self, ctx: &CommandPluginContext<'_>) -> String`
- `async fn cmd(&self, args: Vec<String>) -> Message`
- `async fn cmd(&self, ctx: &CommandPluginContext<'_>, args: Vec<String>) -> CommandPluginSignal`

返回值自动转换：`&str`/`String` → Reply(text)，`Message` → Reply(msg)，`Result<T,E>` → Ok转T

## 信号

- CommandPluginSignal: `Reply(Message)` | `Continue` | `Block(Message)` | `Ignore`
- SystemPluginSignal: `Continue` | `Reply(Message)` | `ApproveFriend{flag,remark}` | `RejectFriend{flag,reason}` | `ApproveGroupInvite{flag,sub_type}` | `Block(Message)` | `Ignore`

## 上下文

- CommandPluginContext: `sender_id()`, `group_id_i64()`, `is_group()`, `is_private()`, `plain_text()`, `message()`, `onebot_actions()`
- event: `sender_nickname()`, `sender_role()`, `message_id()`, `is_at_self()`, `is_group_admin_or_owner()`
- SystemPluginContext: `bot_id`, `event`(原始JSON), `onebot_actions()`

## 消息

```rust
Message::builder().text("文本").at("QQ号").image("URL").face("1").reply(id).keyboard(kb).build()
```

KeyboardBuilder: `.command_button("标签", "/cmd")`, `.jump_button("标签", "url")`, `.row()`, `.build()`

## OneBot API

```rust
let actions = ctx.onebot_actions();
actions.send_group_msg(group_id, msg).await
actions.set_group_ban(group_id, user_id, duration).await
actions.get_group_info(group_id, false).await
```

## 拦截器

```rust
pub struct MyInterceptor;
#[async_trait]
impl MessageEventInterceptor for MyInterceptor {
    async fn pre_handle(&self, bot_id: &str, event: &NormalizedEvent) -> bool { true }
}
// 注册：#[module(interceptors = [MyInterceptor])]
```

## 规范

- 中英文双语注释，tracing 日志
- 新插件放 `plugins/`，根 Cargo.toml workspace members 注册
- 参考 `plugins/qimen-plugin-example/src/`
- `cargo check --workspace` 验证
